                        <li>Review of encumbrances, cautions, and charges</li>
                        <li>Verification of land rates, land rent, and statutory compliance</li>
                        <li>Corporate registry registry searches for company-owned land</li>
                        <li>Review of planning approvals and spousal consent requirements</li>
                        <li>Succession, probate, and inheritance considerations</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="p-5 rounded-xl bg-white/5 border border-white/5">
                    <h4 class="text-white font-semibold text-base">3. Drafting and Negotiation</h4>
